these with these red areas, the
brain changes in response

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:18.420
to treatment, look
very different.

00:16:18.420 --> 00:16:21.240
So there's no simple answer
about whether behavioral

00:16:21.240 --> 00:16:25.060
therapy and drug therapy change
the same or different

00:16:25.060 --> 00:16:26.150
things to help people.

00:16:26.150 --> 00:16:29.450
Depends on the disorder,
depends on the drug.

00:16:29.450 --> 00:16:31.510
And we just have a lot more
to learn about that.

00:16:31.510 --> 00:16:34.380
But both of those things affect
the brain and can be

00:16:34.380 --> 00:16:36.250
effective to help people.

00:16:36.250 --> 00:16:38.720
So let's focus on depression
a little bit.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:41.070
These are people with depression
who feel fearful,

00:16:41.070 --> 00:16:43.510
gloomy, helpless, hopeless
in an extreme way.

00:16:43.510 --> 00:16:46.450
So it's difficult to get out of
bed, difficult to do work,

00:16:46.450 --> 00:16:48.800
relate to people.

