00:17:04.599 --> 00:17:05.680
depression.

00:17:05.680 --> 00:17:10.220
A pervasive dysphoria, just
sort of inability to feel

00:17:10.220 --> 00:17:13.200
pleasure and intense
mental pain,

00:17:13.200 --> 00:17:14.599
generalized loss of interest.

00:17:14.599 --> 00:17:18.089
It's estimated to sometimes
affected some 5% of the

00:17:18.089 --> 00:17:19.020
world's population.

00:17:19.020 --> 00:17:21.300
That's a huge number
of individuals.

00:17:21.300 --> 00:17:24.180
Average age of onset is 30.

00:17:24.180 --> 00:17:28.390
But it goes across wide ages,
often unnoticed in children.

00:17:28.390 --> 00:17:30.750
People are picking this up
more than they used to.

00:17:30.750 --> 00:17:32.740
They used to think there's a
thought that children can't

00:17:32.740 --> 00:17:34.380
really be depressed.

00:17:34.380 --> 00:17:36.310
It's hard to know why that
happened exactly.

00:17:36.310 --> 00:17:39.770
Psychiatric ideas are typically
developed in adults.

00:17:39.770 --> 00:17:41.270
And it takes a while
for the field to

00:17:41.270 --> 00:17:43.570
recognize them in children.

00:17:43.570 --> 00:17:46.200
But it's rare to have a first
depressive episode after 60.

00:17:46.200 --> 00:17:48.815
It's rare to have gone your life
and then get depression

00:17:48.815 --> 00:17:51.360
in older age.

00:17:51.360 --> 00:17:54.480
Kind of mysteriously at the
moment, women have depression

00:17:54.480 --> 00:17:57.040
at two or three times the rate
of men in the United States,

00:17:57.040 --> 00:17:58.730
and pretty much throughout
the world at a two

00:17:58.730 --> 00:17:59.660
to threefold increase.

00:17:59.660 --> 00:18:01.470
That's a pretty big one.

00:18:01.470 --> 00:18:02.690
We'll talk later about ADHD.

00:18:02.690 --> 00:18:03.875
There the numbers
kind of reverse.

00:18:03.875 --> 00:18:08.130
It's 2 to 3 times more frequent
in boys than girls.

00:18:08.130 --> 00:18:11.270
And about 70% of people who
will have one episode of

00:18:11.270 --> 00:18:13.110
depression will have another
one later on.

