00:19:37.870 --> 00:19:41.130
adolescent or child as simply
moody, they're recognizing

00:19:41.130 --> 00:19:42.220
depression?

00:19:42.220 --> 00:19:46.030
Or is the increased pressures
in childhood driving

00:19:46.030 --> 00:19:47.860
depression up at
an earlier age?

00:19:47.860 --> 00:19:49.330
Very hard to tell.

